  Description: 'Wound: Shrapnel from cannon fire embedded in the abdomen, intestines
    visible, stench rising.


    Story: Matteo, once a fisherman of Birgu, writhes
    in agony as the stench of death already clings to him. He speaks of mornings
    on the sea, his children laughing as they hauled nets. Now he clutches your sleeve,
